  "title": "Vibrant Herbal French Cheese Gratin",
  "description": "A flavorful and healthy French dish featuring shredded monterey jack cheese and a mirepoix base, perfect for a weeknight dinner. This recipe is anti-inflammatory friendly and made in individual ramekins.",
